    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 225400.0,
      "end_time": 228240.0,
      "text": "But how can you not be a part of fake news?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 228680.0,
      "end_time": 235160.0,
      "text": "First, if it's too dramatic, too emotional, too clickbait,"
